{"id":386,"parent_id":381,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":386,"title":"2 Chronicles 5","subtitle":"","short_title":"2 Chr.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/5","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 5"],[".studySummary",["i","The temple is finished, and the ark of the covenant is placed in the holy of holies—The glory of the Lord fills the temple."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/5.1","order":"02.15.005.29462"},["b","1"],"Thus all the work that Solomon made for the house of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"was finished: and Solomon brought in",["i","all"],"the things that David his father had dedicated; and the silver, and the gold, and all the instruments, put he among the treasures of the house of God."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/5.2","order":"02.15.005.29463"},["b","2"],"¶Then Solomon assembled the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"elders"],"of Israel, and all the heads of the tribes, the chief of the fathers of the children of Israel, unto Jerusalem, to bring up the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"ark"],"of the covenant of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"out of the city of David, which",["i","is"],"Zion."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/5.3","order":"02.15.005.29464"},["b","3"],"Wherefore all the men of Israel assembled themselves unto the king in the feast which",["i","was"],"in the seventh month."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/5.4","order":"02.15.005.29465"},["b","4"],"And all the elders of Israel came; and the Levites took up the ark."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/5.5","order":"02.15.005.29466"},["b","5"],"And they brought up the ark, and the tabernacle of the congregation, and all the holy vessels that",["i","were"],"in the tabernacle, these did the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"priests"],["i","and"],"the Levites bring up."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/5.6","order":"02.15.005.29467"},["b","6"],"Also king Solomon, and all the congregation of Israel that were assembled unto him before the ark, sacrificed sheep and oxen, which could not be told nor numbered for multitude."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/5.7","order":"02.15.005.29468"},["b","7"],"And the priests brought in the ark of the covenant of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"unto his place, to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"oracle"],"of the house, into the most holy",["i","place, even"],"under the wings of the cherubims:"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/5.8","order":"02.15.005.29469"},["b","8"],"For the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"cherubims"],"spread forth",["i","their"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"wings"],"over the place of the ark, and the cherubims covered the ark and the staves thereof above."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/5.9","order":"02.15.005.29470"},["b","9"],"And they drew out the staves",["i","of the ark,"],"that the ends of the staves were seen from the ark before the oracle; but they were not seen without. And there it is unto this day."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/5.10","order":"02.15.005.29471"},["b","10"],["i","There was"],"nothing in the ark save the two tables which Moses put",["i","therein"],"at Horeb, when the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"made",["i","a covenant"],"with the children of Israel, when they came out of Egypt."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/5.11","order":"02.15.005.29472"},["b","11"],"¶And it came to pass, when the priests were come out of the holy",["i","place:"],"(for all the priests",["i","that were"],"present were sanctified,",["i","and"],"did not",["i","then"],"wait by course:"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/5.12","order":"02.15.005.29473"},["b","12"],"Also the Levites",["i","which were"],"the singers, all of them of Asaph, of Heman, of Jeduthun, with their sons and their brethren,",["i","being"],"arrayed in white",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"linen"],", having cymbals and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"psalteries"],"and harps, stood at the east end of the altar, and with them an hundred and twenty priests sounding with trumpets:)"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/5.13","order":"02.15.005.29474"},["b","13"],"It came even to pass, as the trumpeters and singers",["i","were"],"as one, to make one sound to be heard in praising and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"thanking"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; and when they lifted up",["i","their"],"voice with the trumpets and cymbals and instruments of musick, and praised the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],",",["i","saying,"],"For",["i","he is"],"good; for his mercy",["i","endureth"],"for ever: that",["i","then"],"the house was filled with a cloud,",["i","even"],"the house of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],";"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/5.14","order":"02.15.005.29475"},["b","14"],"So that the priests could not stand to minister by reason of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"cloud"],": for the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"glory"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"had filled the house of God."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/5.2a","order":"02.15.005.29476"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/8.1.1-11"},"1 Kgs. 8:1 (1–11)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/5.2b","order":"02.15.005.29478"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/ark-of-the-covenant"},"TG Ark of the Covenant"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/5.5a","order":"02.15.005.29480"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/8.3"},"1 Kgs. 8:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/5.7a","order":"02.15.005.29482"},["b","7a"],["span.small","OR"],"inner sanctuary."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/5.8a","order":"02.15.005.29484"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/cherubim"},"TG Cherubim"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/5.8b","order":"02.15.005.29486"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/77.4"},"D&C 77:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/5.12a","order":"02.15.005.29488"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apparel"},"TG Apparel"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/5.12b","order":"02.15.005.29490"},["b","12b"],["span.small","OR"],"lyres."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/5.13a","order":"02.15.005.29492"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/16.41"},"1 Chr. 16:41"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezra/3.11"},"Ezra 3:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/97.13"},"D&C 97:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.28"},"136:28"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/5.14a","order":"02.15.005.29494"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/18.38"},"3 Ne. 18:38"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.5"},"D&C 84:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/5.14b","order":"02.15.005.29496"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/9.15"},"Num. 9:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/7.2.2-3"},"2 Chr. 7:2 (2–3)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/97.15"},"D&C 97:15"],"."]]}
